metadata.description: This NFT has moved! The NFT that used to live here now lives with the NEW Crypto Mo Art Appreciation Society smart contract, which has replaced the original smart contract. For the 127 original minters, your original MO has been airdropped into your wallet (and, for many, you also received a BONUS airdrop!). Please visit your MO at its new home in your wallet. You can also find your Crypto MO NFT on OpenSea at its new collection URL: https://opensea.io/collection/the-crypto-mos. Thanks to all of our OG supporters!! The Crypto Mo relaunch starts on 2-2-22. See out Twitter at https://twitter.com/crypto_mo_nft for details!
metadata.name: (Moved) Crypto Mo #1
